SALTINTESTA █
UPDATED: 2026-07-09

DESCRIPTION
Articulate ideas in as few good words as possible. This skill is built on the idea of prose as 'Saltintesta' from Paul Graham's Write Simply [https://www.paulgraham.com/simply.html]. 

